        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your<strong> wholewheat noodles</strong> to a large pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min</p><p>Drain the<strong> soaked noodles</strong>, and reserve the pot</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681808886392-x200.jpg",
