      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the duck legs are golden and crispy, remove the tray from the oven and transfer the <strong>duck legs</strong> to a clean board</p><p>Shred the <strong>duck meat</strong> apart with two forks, discard the bones – this technique is known as 'pulling' – this is your <strong>pulled duck</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681808900694-x200.jpg",
